              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\nOh, and they even added Bret Victor style variable \"scrubbing\".\n\n(Desktop also got builtin Math Notes, minus handwriting, briefly flashed 51:57 — looks very much like "
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "http://Calca.io",
                "text": "Calca.io"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " / Soulver / NoteCalc etc.?)\n\nSo, are we \"Magic Ink\" yet?  (I'm not so much thinking of Bret Victor's essay as Ink&Switch's experiments like "
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://www.inkandswitch.com/inkbase/"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ", CrossCut & Untangle ...)\nOn one hand nothing revolutionary, spreadsheets had much more power for decades.\nAnd yet a solid chunk of useful functionality is starting to move into taken-for-granted \"this is just how futuristic paper "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "naturally",
                "style": {
                  "italic": true
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " works\" territory "
              },
              {
                "type": "emoji",
                "name": "clap",
                "unicode": "1f44f"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ".\nI expect long term it might make such \"what-if\" explorations accessible¹ to more people, and more importantly prepare people for more complex interactions on top?\n\n¹ well, once/IF it waters down to lower-end hardware.  Good-enough stylus tech remains expensive enough to be niche, "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "not",
                "style": {
                  "italic": true
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " evenly distributed "
              },
